TestSystemTestGoalRunsAllDiscovered
/ Structural guard against the silent-skip regression: system/test.goal must
/ (1) call test.discover and (2) hand the full discovered list to test.run
/ without a foreach. The foreach variant skipped tests silently when a single
/ test errored — that's the whole reason this module was rewritten.
- read file '/system/test.goal', write to %goalText%
- assert %goalText% contains 'test.discover'
- assert %goalText% contains 'test.run'
- assert %goalText% does not contain 'foreach'
